                     <interp inst="t17610401-12-verdict68" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>See him tried last sessions, No. 103. for picking Mr. Clark's pocket, of a handkerchief in Cheapside.</p>
